Uicheon Doryonggi.Description: At the end of the Yuan dynasty, a legend was handed down that 'the one who possesses the invincible weapons, the Uicheon Sword and the Dragon Sword, gains the world and rules the world.' Starting with the story, Jang Mu-gi, who was a little boy, witnessed the tragic end of his parents and sharpened the blade of revenge, depicting the process of becoming a teacher of Myeong-gyo, the conflict and growth that unfolds in it.
